&lt;p&gt;    Building Appveyor right now probably not, since I don&apos;t think we do erlang on windows in our CI right now.  In order to get there, we need erlang support in the cmake build environment.  The travis builds are the important ones, although as we discovered with the tutorials rotting, a build is only as good as what it tests.  Hopefully we have enough tests to cover these changes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
